N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6155.2 - Publications and videotapes

State Regulations

Fees for copies of Bureau of Prosecution Services'
publications and videotapes shall be in amounts not to exceed the estimated
cost of developing, printing and reproducing such materials, plus postage or
shipping, where applicable. A list of current publications available and costs
therefor will be furnished upon request. Contact the Bureau of Prosecution

Services at the Division of Criminal Justice Services, Executive Park Tower, Stuyvesant Plaza, Albany, NY 12203, (518) 457-8413. Notes
